<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Artifact on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/artifact/</link><description>Recent content in Artifact on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/artifact/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Could Not Find Artifact</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/maven/dependency-not-found/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/maven/dependency-not-found/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;This error means Maven looked in all configured repositories (local, central, and custom) but could not find the artifact specified in your &lt;code&gt;pom.xml&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The artifact coordinates (groupId, artifactId, version) are misspelled&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The artifact has been removed from Maven Central or never published&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A custom repository URL is incorrect or requires authentication&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The artifact only exists in a private repository not configured in the build&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Verify the artifact coordinates on &lt;a href="https://search.maven.org"&gt;Maven Central&lt;/a&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Could Not Resolve Dependency — Gradle</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/gradle/gradle-dependency-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/gradle/gradle-dependency-error/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="could-not-resolve-dependency--gradle"&gt;Could Not Resolve Dependency — Gradle&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This error means Gradle looked in all configured repositories (Maven Central, local cache, custom repos) but could not find the artifact specified in your build script. The dependency coordinates or repository configuration are incorrect.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The dependency is misspelled in &lt;code&gt;build.gradle&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The artifact does not exist in the configured repositories&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A custom repository URL is incorrect or requires authentication&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Network issues prevent repository access&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="verify-dependency-coordinates"&gt;Verify Dependency Coordinates&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-groovy" data-lang="groovy"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;dependencies &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; implementation &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;com.example:library:1.0.0&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// check groupId, artifactId, version
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Search &lt;a href="https://search.maven.org"&gt;Maven Central&lt;/a&gt; for the correct coordinates.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>GitHub Actions Artifact Upload Error</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/github-actions/github-actions-artifact-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/github-actions/github-actions-artifact-error/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="github-actions-artifact-upload-error"&gt;GitHub Actions Artifact Upload Error&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An artifact upload error occurs when the &lt;code&gt;actions/upload-artifact&lt;/code&gt; action fails to save workflow artifacts. This can happen due to size limits, path issues, or permission problems.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Artifact size exceeds the 500MB limit per artifact&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;File path does not exist or is incorrect&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Artifact name conflicts with existing artifact&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Permissions issue with artifact storage&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="check-file-path-exists"&gt;Check File Path Exists&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;- &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;Upload build output&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;uses&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;actions/upload-artifact@v4&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;with&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;build-output&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;path&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;dist/&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="reduce-artifact-size"&gt;Reduce Artifact Size&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;- &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;Upload artifact&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;uses&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;actions/upload-artifact@v4&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;with&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;build-output&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;path&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;dist/&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;compression-level&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;6&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Higher compression&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="use-multiple-smaller-artifacts"&gt;Use Multiple Smaller Artifacts&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;- &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;Upload JS artifacts&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;uses&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;actions/upload-artifact@v4&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;with&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;js-bundle&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;path&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;dist/*.js&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;- &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;Upload CSS artifacts&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;uses&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;actions/upload-artifact@v4&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;css-bundle&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;path&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;dist/*.css&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-artifact-name-conflicts"&gt;Fix Artifact Name Conflicts&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;- &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;Upload artifact&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;uses&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;actions/upload-artifact@v4&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;with&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;build-${{ github.run_number }} &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Use unique name&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;path&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;dist/&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="check-permissions"&gt;Check Permissions&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;permissions&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;contents&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;read&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;actions&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;write&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Error: path does not exist&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;- &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;uses&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;actions/upload-artifact@v4&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;with&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;build&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;path&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;/nonexistent/path&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Error: artifact too large&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;Error&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;Artifact size (600MB) exceeds maximum allowed (500MB)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/github-actions/github-actions-cache-error/"&gt;Cache Error&lt;/a&gt; — cache operation failure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/github-actions/github-actions-timeout-error/"&gt;Timeout Error&lt;/a&gt; — job timeout&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>GitHub Actions Artifact Upload Failed</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/github-actions/github-actions-artifact-error-v2/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/github-actions/github-actions-artifact-error-v2/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="github-actions--artifact-upload-failed"&gt;GitHub Actions — Artifact Upload Failed&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This error occurs when the &lt;code&gt;actions/upload-artifact&lt;/code&gt; action fails to upload an artifact. The artifact may be too large, the path may be incorrect, or the workflow may lack permissions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Artifact path does not exist&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Artifact size exceeds limit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Multiple artifacts with the same name&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Workflow permissions insufficient&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Disk space issue on runner&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="verify-artifact-path-exists"&gt;Verify Artifact Path Exists&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;- &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;run&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;ls -la dist/&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;- &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;uses&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;actions/upload-artifact@v4&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;with&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;build-output&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;path&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;dist/&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="set-artifact-name-uniquely"&gt;Set Artifact Name Uniquely&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;- &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;uses&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;actions/upload-artifact@v4&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;with&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;build-${{ github.run_number }}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;path&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;dist/&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="configure-artifact-retention"&gt;Configure Artifact Retention&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;- &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;uses&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;actions/upload-artifact@v4&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;with&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;coverage-report&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;path&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;coverage/&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;retention-days&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;7&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="check-artifact-size"&gt;Check Artifact Size&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;du -sh dist/
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="download-artifact-in-another-job"&gt;Download Artifact in Another Job&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;- &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;uses&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;actions/download-artifact@v4&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;with&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;build-output&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;path&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;dist/&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-text" data-lang="text"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Error: Artifact with name &amp;#39;build-output&amp;#39; already exists for this workflow run.
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/github-actions/github-actions-cache-error/"&gt;GitHub Actions Cache Error&lt;/a&gt; — cache restore failure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/github-actions/github-actions-permission-error/"&gt;GitHub Actions Permission Error&lt;/a&gt; — permission issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/github-actions/github-actions-runner-error/"&gt;GitHub Actions Runner Error&lt;/a&gt; — runner issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>Maven Could Not Find Artifact in Repository</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/maven/maven-dependency-error-v2/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/maven/maven-dependency-error-v2/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="maven-could-not-find-artifact-in-repository"&gt;Maven Could Not Find Artifact in Repository&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This error occurs when Maven cannot locate a required artifact in any configured repository. The build stops because a declared dependency is unavailable at the specified coordinates.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Artifact groupId, artifactId, or version is misspelled&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Artifact does not exist in Maven Central or configured repos&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Custom repository URL is incorrect&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Repository requires authentication that is not configured&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Network issues preventing repository access&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="verify-artifact-exists"&gt;Verify Artifact Exists&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;mvn dependency:get -Dartifact&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;com.example:library:1.0.0
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="search-maven-central"&gt;Search Maven Central&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Visit &lt;a href="https://search.maven.org"&gt;search.maven.org&lt;/a&gt; and verify the correct coordinates.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Maven Dependency Resolution Error</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/maven/maven-dependency-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/maven/maven-dependency-error/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="maven-dependency-resolution-error"&gt;Maven Dependency Resolution Error&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Maven dependency resolution error means Maven searched all configured repositories but could not find the artifact specified in the &lt;code&gt;pom.xml&lt;/code&gt;. The build cannot proceed without the required dependency.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The artifact coordinates (groupId, artifactId, version) are misspelled&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The artifact does not exist in Maven Central or custom repositories&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A custom repository URL is incorrect or requires authentication&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Network issues prevent repository access&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Local repository cache is corrupted&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="verify-artifact-coordinates"&gt;Verify Artifact Coordinates&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;mvn dependency:get -Dartifact&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;com.example:library:1.0.0
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="check-maven-central"&gt;Check Maven Central&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Search &lt;a href="https://search.maven.org"&gt;Maven Central&lt;/a&gt; for the correct artifact coordinates.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>